      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7889&rangeEnd=7935",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7889&rangeEnd=7935"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_3_2375-2434",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2375-2434",
      "markText": "宋太祖为强化其中央专制集权统治而施行的崇文抑武、偏重防内的国策，也对整个宋代“积弱”局面的形成，有着颇为深刻的负面影响",
