      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2375&rangeEnd=2434",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2375&rangeEnd=2434"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_3_1313-1365",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1313-1365",
      "markText": "杀人盈野，赤地千里，无辜百姓流离失所，社会生产力遭到前所未有的大破坏，成为中国历史上至为黑暗、动荡的时期",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_10_19503-19715",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "19503-19715",
      "markText": "此役周军死伤惨重，周世宗盛怒之下，发令屠城，欲以警戒天下敢于与周军拼到玉石俱焚者，结果城中军民被杀者万余人，官署民房皆被焚毁。史籍誉称周世宗为“五代第一明君”，但这一残暴行为，实在有辱“明君”之号。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=19503&rangeEnd=19715",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=19503&rangeEnd=19715"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_17_18925-18992",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "18925-18992",
      "markText": "因此，宋太祖这种一推一拉的手法，表面上是在安抚李重进之心，实质是迫使其起兵谋反，好让自己师出有名，一举解决掉李重进，除去心中又一大患。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=18925&rangeEnd=18992",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=18925&rangeEnd=18992"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_20_3795-3879",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3795-3879",
      "markText": "但这也带来了颇为严重的负面结果，即宋军在与辽军以及此后与西夏军队作战时，领兵将领因为缺少自己信得过的牙兵卫队，往往战死沙场，或被敌人所擒获。这大概是宋太祖所始料不及的。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3795&rangeEnd=3879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3795&rangeEnd=3879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_10_8858-8911",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "8858-8911",
      "markText": "太祖皇帝拥马颈突陈而入，大呼曰：“吾止取皇甫晖，它人非吾敌也！”手剑击晖，中脑，生擒之，并擒姚凤，遂克滁州",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8858&rangeEnd=8911",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=8858&rangeEnd=8911"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_24_10839-10923",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "10839-10923",
      "markText": "虽说宋太祖贵为天子，但仍是一个食烟火的尘世凡人，宠爱容颜绝世的佳人也属人之常情，况且是对降王有生杀予夺大权的皇上，然而为得到一绝色美人，杀其夫而夺其妻，终究有欠光明磊落",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10839&rangeEnd=10923",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=10839&rangeEnd=10923"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080172_14_6650-6739",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "6650-6739",
      "markText": "对于陈桥兵变的发生，元代之后，世人大都指出兵变乃是赵匡胤、赵普等事先策划、精心布置的结果，但宋人却几乎异口同声地声称是出自“天命”所归，宋太祖赵匡胤完全是被动地接受“黄袍加身”。",
      "totalCount": 56,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080172&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6650&rangeEnd=6739",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ba326f0813ab85d1g012986?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=6650&rangeEnd=6739"
    },
    {
